snippet.title: Super Cat Tales: PAWS - Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Super Cat Tales: PAWS is the newest adventure in the Super Cat Tales series.

This time you join the PAWS team, an elite force of cats on a secret mission to protect Neko Land. As the main cat characters, you can explore a multitude of levels full of secrets, play new minigames, and complete side quests for a Super Cat Tales game more engaging than ever before.
